# Plan §13.6, any change to a TCB-core file requires TWO reviewers;
# this file is the request-for-review surface, not the merge-block.
# Full enforcement (the merge-block) requires a GitHub
# branch-protection rule, which is repository-administrator
# territory and out-of-scope for a code-only PR.
#
# CODEOWNERS syntax: <path-pattern> <space-separated reviewers>.
# Reviewers are GitHub usernames or teams.  See
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-security/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# IMPORTANT.  The handles below name @hatter6822 (project owner) as
